3. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) - The paper discusses the importance of cyber security and detecting adversarial activities, indicating a focus on security and cryptography. 
4. cs.DB (Databases) - The paper involves processing and analyzing large-scale data in real-time, which is a common problem in database systems. 
5. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper involves analyzing network traffic streams, indicating a focus on networking and internet architecture.
